Amelia Vargas

Hi! I’m Amelia, a data scientist based in the Pacific Northwest.

I work for SAIF, Oregon’s not-for-profit workers’ compensation insurance company, solving hard problems with creativity and a human-centered approach. Prior to SAIF, I proudly served the State of Oregon as a Senior Research Analyst for many years.

I’m passionate about supporting organizations in the adoption and evolution of tools and frameworks to make life better for data nerds and math geeks.

I’m currently interested in learning Julia and this might be the year I finally start blogging.

Organizations

I’m a member of the State of Oregon Research Academy (SORA) Executive Committee.
